      "text": "Type: Anti-diarrheal,\nopioid\nDosage Forms: 1mg, 2mg; 1/5 mL\nRoutes of Administration: PO\nCommon Trade Names: Imodium, Diamode, Imodium A-D, Imodium A-D EZ Chews, Imodium A-D New Formula, Kao-Paverin, Kaopectate 1-D",
